      "comment": "MYSTIC MOTIVER (1) has been good from wider barriers in all three starts to date. Only missed narrowly as runner-up at her first two starts, one of them at this circuit and distance, before a 3.5m fourth at her latest appearance at Kilmore. Gets her chance from the ace draw. ALLGOOD VINNIE (12) drew deep and started poorly last start so the effort to finish fifth had some merit. With his A-game and even luck from the back row he could win a race like this. WICKED ONE (6) is heading the right way, improving last time out to finish second after racing parked at Shepparton. Last-start placegetter JACQUELYN JOY (2) should not have any excuses from the favourable draw.",
